data.description: Charming townhome in Pooler! Step into your well-kept, two-story end unit with community clubhouse and pool in the Carriage Square Homes subdivision. Located conveniently off Pooler Parkway, this 3 Bedroom 2.5 bath home offers serenity while suitably accessible to all that Pooler, Chatham and surrounding counties have to offer. The first floor boasts hardwood floors in the hallway, formal dining room and powder room. The kitchen opens to a large living room, which has French doors to the patio. Master bedroom with ensuite and walk-in closet, two guest bedrooms and additional full bathroom are all upstairs. Patio and parking in the rear of the unit. Dont miss out on this captivating townhome. Sold as-is and priced to sell. Schedule a private tour before its gone!
